  "body": "<p>Truly one of the best parts of what I do for work (how lucky am I to have this job?!) is meeting creative and kind people. I am always humbled by their enthusiasm and kind words. Some of them even ask me to sign stuff! (Blushing). So when the opportunity presents itself - an owner reaching out and inviting me to their store to teach classes - my heart skips a beat. Tammy, the spunky owner of <a href=\"http://www.paperniche.com/\">Paper Niche</a> reached out a couple months ago and amidst all the craziness, we planned a class for Friday night and 2 classes on Saturday. There were even a few people who signed up for all 3 classes. We played with <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_mister%2520huey%2527s_/\">Studio Calico Mister Hueys</a>, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/126957-cascade-amy-tangerine-sketchbook-scene-glitter-foam-thickers-stickers/%3Ffilters%3D_thickers_\">Thickers</a>, watercolors, <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_mistable_/stickers/\">Mistables</a> and all kinds of fun stuff. How lucky I was to spend the bulk of my weekend surrounded by crafty hands and smiling faces.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"6a-IMG_0094-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600643732511-5UE783L5CNGWIVXNO7VE/6a-IMG_0094-600x450.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"6b-IMG_0099-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600643732520-EXEA52TLMTDC0ABRC0Y7/6b-IMG_0099-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6c-IMG_0102-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600643733231-AZWAMGAL9NFGFIF97K1G/6c-IMG_0102-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6d-Untitled-1-600x399.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600643733243-SPMLCCA7WL9X2FI66JUK/6d-Untitled-1-600x399.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6e-IMG_0108-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600643733609-LSVNU9NY2SJTTYUXNOHK/6e-IMG_0108-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6f-IMG_0113-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600643733755-UW4YYBYCSHASMV87YL1T/6f-IMG_0113-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6g-IMG_0120-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600643734042-BG0G6XJMR10B6DM4CPZZ/6g-IMG_0120-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6h-IMG_0117-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600643734587-R3OMSVSN6H1MPPEPJGYC/6h-IMG_0117-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6i-IMG_0134-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600643734639-JA90FSZRDP2ASP7V83OC/6i-IMG_0134-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6j-IMG_0136-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600643735070-1QFX6YU9KUUMRWBQLFW9/6j-IMG_0136-600x450.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6k-IMG_0139-600x450.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600643735135-2R6QDC0LSADI6JGZMON5/6k-IMG_0139-600x450.jpg\"/>"
